<h1>Couch Paint</h1>

<p>
  Just playing around with <a href="https://ember-twiddle.com/9000b38fe719e05499f88edff5b50265" title="SVG Animation and Interaction">SVG</a> and <a href="https://www.cloudstation.com/en" title="CloudStation">CloudStation</a>. I you want to improve something write a <a href="https://github.com/broerse/couch-paint" title="GitHub Source">PR on GitHub</a>. Thanks!
</p>

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="800px" height="600px" viewBox="0 0 80 60">
  <g {{action 'paint'}}>
    {{#if showRects}}{{svg-rects rects=model }}{{/if}}
  </g>
</svg>

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100px" height="100px" viewBox="0 0 1 1">
  <rect fill={{color}} x="0" y="0" width="1" height="1" />
</svg>

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="300px" height="300px" viewBox="0 0 18 18">
  <g {{action 'pick'}}>
    {{svg-rects rects=pick }}
  </g>
</svg>

{{outlet}}
